    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add <strong>half</strong> of your <strong>Marmite</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) to a small bowl with your<strong> chilli relish</strong>, <strong>peanut butter </strong>and <strong>soy sauce </strong>and mix until combined – this is your <strong>Marmite satay sauce</strong></p>",
