    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your<strong> spinach</strong>, then pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Once the pork has caramelised, add your <strong>udon noodles </strong>and <strong>spinach</strong> to the pan with 1 tbsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]<strong> </span>water</strong> and cook, covered, for 2 min until the spinach has started to wilt and the pork is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p><p>Tip: Gently separate the noodles with a fork!</p>",
